1
00:00:05,717 --> 00:00:08,413
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,486 --> 00:00:12,354
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,423 --> 00:00:16,416
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,761 --> 00:00:19,252
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,330 --> 00:00:23,391
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,468 --> 00:00:27,427
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,906 --> 00:00:33,639
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,345 --> 00:00:37,314
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,751 --> 00:00:41,844
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,587 --> 00:00:43,884
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,222 --> 00:00:46,782
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,832 --> 00:01:00,202
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,404 --> 00:01:01,564
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,639 --> 00:01:05,439
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,777 --> 00:01:10,976
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,249 --> 00:01:12,580
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,650 --> 00:01:14,049
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,118 --> 00:01:20,387
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:31,670 --> 00:01:35,834
<i>There is no way that I alone can</i>
<i>lose in a place like this!</i>

20
00:01:36,408 --> 00:01:38,899
<i>Guy Sensei... please allow it.</i>

21
00:01:39,945 --> 00:01:41,173
<i>It is now...</i>

22
00:01:49,955 --> 00:01:54,085
<i>A time to carry through and protect</i>
<i>one's own Way of the Ninja!</i>

23
00:01:54,560 --> 00:02:00,260
The Fifth Gate: A Splendid Ninja is Born

24
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,160
The color of his body changed...!

25
00:02:05,904 --> 00:02:06,768
He's red?!

26
00:02:14,746 --> 00:02:16,077
What's up with him?!

27
00:02:19,985 --> 00:02:22,078
He's opened the third gate,
the Gate of Life...

28
00:02:23,021 --> 00:02:23,817
He's going to make his move!

29
00:02:24,122 --> 00:02:25,612
No, not yet!

30
00:02:25,858 --> 00:02:26,586
What?!

31
00:02:30,562 --> 00:02:31,426
<i>And also,</i>

32
00:02:31,964 --> 00:02:35,161
<i>the fourth gate,</i>
<i>the Gate of Pain... open!</i>

33
00:02:42,207 --> 00:02:43,174
<i>What an incredible guy...</i>

34
00:02:44,476 --> 00:02:46,569
<i>It's not as though effort alone</i>
<i>can make this happen...</i>

35
00:02:47,546 --> 00:02:48,171
<i>That boy...</i>

36
00:02:49,014 --> 00:02:50,311
<i>is he in fact a genius...?</i>

37
00:03:02,261 --> 00:03:02,955
<i>He's fast!</i>

38
00:03:06,431 --> 00:03:07,193
Gaara!

39
00:03:07,266 --> 00:03:07,960
Where are they?!

40
00:03:10,002 --> 00:03:10,798
He's above!

41
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,167
But we can't find Lee!

42
00:03:17,809 --> 00:03:18,707
Where?!

43
00:03:24,850 --> 00:03:27,978
<i>The sand isn't keeping up at all!</i>

44
00:03:35,861 --> 00:03:37,590
<i>So it's the Sand Armor again...?</i>

45
00:03:39,031 --> 00:03:41,556
<i>Then how's this?!</i>

46
00:03:51,143 --> 00:03:52,132
<i>What...?!</i>

47
00:03:52,878 --> 00:03:54,539
<i>This Sand Armor is...</i>

48
00:03:57,783 --> 00:03:59,182
<i>being peeled away...!</i>

49
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,912
<i>You're a stubborn one.</i>

50
00:04:04,957 --> 00:04:06,083
<i>Since it comes to this...</i>

51
00:04:11,263 --> 00:04:12,855
<i>The muscles have torn...</i>

52
00:04:16,201 --> 00:04:17,498
<i>Is that really Lee...?</i>

53
00:04:18,270 --> 00:04:19,464
<i>When did he become like this...?</i>

54
00:04:23,175 --> 00:04:24,836
This is the end!

55
00:04:25,777 --> 00:04:28,439
<i>The Fifth Gate of Closing...open!</i>

56
00:04:31,183 --> 00:04:32,844
<i>I can't defend myself...</i>

57
00:04:33,452 --> 00:04:35,511
<i>Is this the movement of</i>
<i>a human being?!</i>

58
00:04:37,155 --> 00:04:37,883
<i>Neji...</i>

59
00:04:39,191 --> 00:04:41,625
<i>This technique is my ace in</i>
<i>the hole to take you down...</i>

60
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,558
<i>but I will specially show it to you!</i>

61
00:04:47,232 --> 00:04:47,994
Huh?!

62
00:05:04,349 --> 00:05:06,214
<i>The Sand Shield can't keep up!</i>

63
00:05:06,752 --> 00:05:08,617
<i>Most of the armor has also</i>
<i>been peeled off...</i>

64
00:05:09,154 --> 00:05:10,018
<i>He's done for!</i>

65
00:05:10,489 --> 00:05:11,888
<i>W-Wow!</i>

66
00:05:12,624 --> 00:05:14,717
<i>Hidden Lotus... In other words...</i>

67
00:05:14,793 --> 00:05:17,523
<i>it's a high speed continuous</i>
<i>Taijutsu that can't even be touched!</i>

68
00:05:18,063 --> 00:05:21,191
<i>The answer to take Neji down is</i>
<i>that high speed combination...</i>

69
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,663
<i>There is no way that</i>
<i>the sand can keep up!</i>

70
00:05:24,736 --> 00:05:26,499
<i>This technique will be the last!</i>

71
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:33,941
Hidden Lotus!

72
00:05:42,988 --> 00:05:45,684
<i>I can't see anything, it's too fast...</i>

73
00:05:58,003 --> 00:05:58,935
<i>That's impossible...</i>

74
00:05:59,538 --> 00:06:01,005
<i>The gourd has turned to sand...?</i>

75
00:06:09,648 --> 00:06:11,115
He's done it this time!

76
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:12,314
Gaara!

77
00:06:13,585 --> 00:06:14,210
Lee...

78
00:06:19,291 --> 00:06:20,223
Oh!

79
00:06:20,358 --> 00:06:22,087
What's... that?

80
00:06:37,075 --> 00:06:39,100
<i>He protects himself...</i>

81
00:06:40,312 --> 00:06:42,177
<i>using a gourd made of sand?!</i>

82
00:07:03,235 --> 00:07:04,167
<i>That technique is...!</i>

83
00:07:05,537 --> 00:07:06,902
<i>Sand Coffin!</i>

84
00:07:21,753 --> 00:07:22,617
<i>No way!</i>

85
00:07:23,321 --> 00:07:24,583
<i>He got hit by the Hidden Lotus</i>

86
00:07:24,656 --> 00:07:27,216
<i>and is still able to bring</i>
<i>forth a technique...!</i>

87
00:07:37,502 --> 00:07:38,901
Sand Coffin!

88
00:07:47,045 --> 00:07:50,378
<i>I just can not lose in a place like this...</i>

89
00:07:53,051 --> 00:07:53,745
<i>I want to...</i>

90
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:56,082
<i>my Way of the Ninja...</i>

91
00:08:07,699 --> 00:08:08,324
<i>Oh no!</i>

92
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,092
Die!

93
00:08:51,676 --> 00:08:52,734
Why...?

94
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:57,972
Why... save him?

95
00:09:00,819 --> 00:09:01,911
He's...

96
00:09:05,824 --> 00:09:07,086
<i>I'm all right!</i>

97
00:09:07,158 --> 00:09:08,716
<i>I'm strong so...</i>

98
00:09:09,594 --> 00:09:10,686
<i>The Chunin Exam...</i>

99
00:09:10,895 --> 00:09:13,261
<i>Guy Sensei, please watch</i>
<i>me with a smile...</i>

100
00:09:14,165 --> 00:09:16,963
<i>I'd like to prove that I could</i>
<i>become a respectable Ninja</i>

101
00:09:17,035 --> 00:09:19,503
<i>even though I can't use Ninjutsu!</i>

102
00:09:19,971 --> 00:09:21,962
<i>That would be the ultimate for me!</i>

103
00:09:23,642 --> 00:09:24,939
He is...

104
00:09:29,047 --> 00:09:32,744
an important subordinate
whom I care for!

105
00:09:45,505 --> 00:09:48,099
A subordinate... whom I care for?

106
00:09:49,676 --> 00:09:53,544
<i>Those words are definitely</i>
<i>not understandable to Gaara...</i>

107
00:10:00,753 --> 00:10:01,845
I quit...

108
00:10:04,190 --> 00:10:05,657
He quit?

109
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:09,824
The moment Guy jumped in,
Lee lost.

110
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,167
The winner...

111
00:10:15,335 --> 00:10:16,359
Gaa!

112
00:10:16,669 --> 00:10:17,533
- Wha...?
- Huh?

113
00:10:18,471 --> 00:10:19,460
- Huh?
- Huh?

114
00:10:19,739 --> 00:10:20,569
Wha?!

115
00:10:32,452 --> 00:10:33,316
That's impossible...

116
00:10:50,703 --> 00:10:52,000
<i>Having opened the fifth gate...</i>

117
00:10:52,438 --> 00:10:54,429
<i>And his hand and feet are crushed...</i>

118
00:10:55,141 --> 00:10:56,438
<i>There's no way he should</i>
<i>be able to stand...!</i>

119
00:10:59,278 --> 00:10:59,903
Lee...

120
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,109
It's all right.

121
00:11:01,514 --> 00:11:02,446
It's over!

122
00:11:02,882 --> 00:11:04,816
You're in no condition to stand...!

123
00:11:09,222 --> 00:11:10,018
Lee...

124
00:11:11,190 --> 00:11:12,452
Y-You...

125
00:11:14,827 --> 00:11:16,158
You are...

126
00:11:24,737 --> 00:11:26,728
Even after having
lost consciousness...

127
00:11:27,573 --> 00:11:31,270
You still want to prove your
own Way of the Ninja...?

128
00:11:36,215 --> 00:11:37,307
<i>So he had already...</i>

129
00:11:38,284 --> 00:11:39,683
<i>Iost consciousness...</i>

130
00:11:43,489 --> 00:11:44,183
Lee...

131
00:11:46,359 --> 00:11:47,690
You're already...

132
00:11:54,934 --> 00:11:56,492
a respectable Ninja...!

133
00:12:01,207 --> 00:12:01,969
The winner...

134
00:12:02,508 --> 00:12:03,236
Gaara.

135
00:12:17,857 --> 00:12:18,551
Lee!

136
00:12:18,791 --> 00:12:19,553
Stop!

137
00:12:21,861 --> 00:12:23,590
Even if you went down
what could you do?

138
00:12:29,035 --> 00:12:33,062
Your words of encouragement
would only make him feel worse.

139
00:12:46,986 --> 00:12:48,886
There's no way he could
have beaten Gaara...

140
00:12:53,893 --> 00:12:56,794
<i>He was faced with a tougher battle</i>
<i>than we thought...</i>

141
00:13:02,935 --> 00:13:04,095
<i>That Naruto...</i>

142
00:13:11,878 --> 00:13:15,177
<i>Bushy Brow lost</i>
<i>to a guy like this...!</i>

143
00:13:17,950 --> 00:13:19,747
Medics, please hurry.

144
00:13:26,225 --> 00:13:27,385
Bushy Brow...

145
00:13:33,866 --> 00:13:34,730
<i>Lee...</i>

146
00:13:55,788 --> 00:13:58,086
You are the Jonin in charge of him,
aren't you?

147
00:13:59,125 --> 00:14:00,683
Y-Yes.

148
00:14:01,694 --> 00:14:03,025
Please come with me
for a minute.

149
00:14:09,001 --> 00:14:09,831
Careful...

150
00:14:10,770 --> 00:14:11,566
Don't shake him.

151
00:14:26,385 --> 00:14:28,285
There is faint breathing...

152
00:14:28,654 --> 00:14:31,953
but because of comminuted fractures
and muscle tears to his entire body,

153
00:14:32,458 --> 00:14:36,019
recovery will likely to take
quite some time...

154
00:14:39,365 --> 00:14:41,890
If that was all, it wouldn't be so bad, but...

155
00:14:47,540 --> 00:14:50,839
The damage to the left arm
and leg which received the attack is severe...

156
00:14:51,944 --> 00:14:52,842
It's too severe...

157
00:14:53,479 --> 00:14:54,104
<i>Oh...!</i>

158
00:15:00,486 --> 00:15:03,046
I don't want to say this,

159
00:15:04,590 --> 00:15:09,118
but he won't be able to...
live as a Shinobi again.

160
00:15:20,606 --> 00:15:22,540
T-That...

161
00:15:23,242 --> 00:15:25,233
that can't be true...

162
00:15:25,845 --> 00:15:28,541
<i>I will take Bushy Brow down.</i>
<i>Believe it!</i>

163
00:15:28,981 --> 00:15:32,815
<i>It is not you whom I want to fight,</i>
<i>it's Uchiha!</i>

164
00:15:35,087 --> 00:15:35,985
<i>You...!</i>

165
00:15:36,255 --> 00:15:39,315
<i>Naruto, I get where you're</i>
<i>coming from, believe me.</i>

166
00:15:39,825 --> 00:15:43,283
<i>But all fighting must be done</i>
<i>officially in a match!</i>

167
00:15:43,629 --> 00:15:47,121
<i>The failure beats the gifted genius</i>
<i>through sheer effort...</i>

168
00:15:48,234 --> 00:15:49,929
<i>Wouldn't that make for</i>
<i>an exciting main battle?</i>

169
00:15:50,770 --> 00:15:54,331
<i>Though, I am probably going</i>
<i>to be the one fighting Neji...</i>

170
00:15:58,344 --> 00:15:59,038
<i>Lee...</i>

171
00:16:00,146 --> 00:16:04,845
<i>I didn't want to think...that you'd lose.</i>

172
00:16:06,252 --> 00:16:07,879
<i>I wanted to let you fulfill...</i>

173
00:16:09,355 --> 00:16:10,982
<i>your Way of the Ninja!</i>

174
00:16:12,758 --> 00:16:13,918
<i>Yay!</i>

175
00:16:14,126 --> 00:16:16,094
<i>I finally mastered it!</i>

176
00:16:16,429 --> 00:16:17,396
<i>Yahoo!</i>

177
00:16:18,064 --> 00:16:19,326
This technique...

178
00:16:19,398 --> 00:16:22,196
after all, only Lee managed to master...

179
00:16:23,069 --> 00:16:26,368
<i>Okay, you became Genin</i>
<i>from today.</i>

180
00:16:27,073 --> 00:16:29,769
<i>I want to hear what it is</i>
<i>you all are aiming for!</i>

181
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:36,111
<i>I-I'd like to prove that I can become</i>
<i>a respectable Ninja</i>

182
00:16:36,449 --> 00:16:39,384
<i>even though I can't use</i>
<i>Ninjutsu or Genjutsu!</i>

183
00:16:40,186 --> 00:16:42,313
<i>That would be the ultimate for me!</i>

184
00:16:43,789 --> 00:16:46,417
<i>Please forgive me for not...</i>

185
00:16:48,227 --> 00:16:49,421
<i>stopping it...!</i>

186
00:16:51,297 --> 00:16:51,956
<i>Lee...</i>

187
00:16:54,967 --> 00:16:57,458
It's not true... it's not true.

188
00:16:58,404 --> 00:17:02,773
After hearing that,
what should Bushy Brow do...?!

189
00:17:03,976 --> 00:17:04,943
This guy...

190
00:17:05,311 --> 00:17:09,441
He said the failure would take
down a genius with effort!

191
00:17:10,216 --> 00:17:12,343
Isn't there something that
can be done?!

192
00:17:14,153 --> 00:17:15,450
Calm down, Naruto.

193
00:17:16,589 --> 00:17:19,114
B-But... Kakashi Sensei!

194
00:17:19,191 --> 00:17:23,389
He kept saying he wanted
to battle Sasuke and Neji!

195
00:17:23,462 --> 00:17:26,556
Perhaps... that led to his ruin.

196
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:30,626
To fulfill that dream...

197
00:17:30,870 --> 00:17:33,839
the boy even used a self-sacrificing
forbidden technique to try to win!

198
00:17:40,913 --> 00:17:42,847
The result is what you see...

199
00:17:48,087 --> 00:17:49,349
That boy...

200
00:17:49,789 --> 00:17:51,120
Sasuke and Neji...

201
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:52,750
and you...

202
00:17:53,726 --> 00:17:56,752
he sacrificed himself to
a promise he never spoke of.

203
00:17:58,230 --> 00:17:59,720
He risked his life...

204
00:18:00,433 --> 00:18:03,300
so that he might have
a chance to battle you guys...

205
00:18:09,775 --> 00:18:11,333
Don't forget that...

206
00:18:20,453 --> 00:18:21,477
<i>I wonder if Lee...</i>

207
00:18:21,687 --> 00:18:23,120
<i>will be all right...?</i>

208
00:18:28,561 --> 00:18:29,323
<i>Lee...</i>

209
00:18:30,062 --> 00:18:32,462
<i>You didn't realize it even at the end...</i>

210
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:36,324
<i>Heaven does not allow it.</i>

211
00:18:36,402 --> 00:18:39,098
<i>One who tries to move ahead</i>
<i>while achieving victory</i>

212
00:18:39,538 --> 00:18:43,634
<i>through a method like dying</i>
<i>upon each other's swords.</i>

213
00:19:00,192 --> 00:19:03,389
<i>So it ended without incident...</i>

214
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:05,957
Welcome back Gaara.

215
00:19:25,251 --> 00:19:25,979
Guy...

216
00:19:26,752 --> 00:19:27,480
Well...

217
00:19:27,586 --> 00:19:29,486
I spoke self importantly earlier but...

218
00:19:30,789 --> 00:19:34,555
I've thought about it and
had I been in your position...

219
00:19:35,928 --> 00:19:39,455
I probably... wouldn't have
been able to stop him.

220
00:19:45,604 --> 00:19:46,434
Guy.

221
00:19:47,006 --> 00:19:50,305
We're in the way of the
next tournament... let's go up.

222
00:19:54,246 --> 00:19:54,940
All right...

223
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:05,489
Then, the tenth and final round is next,
both contestants come forward!

224
00:20:08,561 --> 00:20:10,426
<i>So it's finally my turn...</i>

225
00:20:14,533 --> 00:20:17,593
<i>I'm gonna win and have</i>
<i>some barbecued beef!</i>

226
00:20:18,637 --> 00:20:22,903
<i>In any case, I need to last until</i>
<i>the main tournament and battle Sasuke.</i>

227
00:20:24,009 --> 00:20:28,708
<i>Or I will not have met your expectations,</i>
<i>Lord Orochimaru...</i>

228
00:20:29,615 --> 00:20:32,106
<i>I can almost see through it...</i>

229
00:20:33,085 --> 00:20:36,020
<i>The reason that you went to the trouble</i>
<i>of getting to Sasuke before us and...</i>

230
00:20:36,522 --> 00:20:39,355
<i>putting a Curse Mark on him</i>
<i>without killing him...</i>

231
00:20:39,992 --> 00:20:41,584
<i>In other words,</i>

232
00:20:41,961 --> 00:20:46,421
<i>we were the guinea pigs to measure</i>
<i>Sasuke's abilities during the examinations.</i>

233
00:20:47,266 --> 00:20:51,930
<i>What you wanted isn't Sasuke's life,</i>
<i>but Sasuke himself...</i>

234
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:56,274
<i>I was also taken for a fool...</i>

235
00:20:59,511 --> 00:21:02,241
Now, let the tenth round begin.

236
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:12,280
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

237
00:21:12,424 --> 00:21:20,763
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

238
00:21:21,767 --> 00:21:30,436
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

239
00:21:30,843 --> 00:21:38,682
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

240
00:21:39,952 --> 00:21:45,356
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

241
00:21:45,424 --> 00:21:49,451
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

242
00:21:49,528 --> 00:21:53,089
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

243
00:21:53,432 --> 00:22:01,965
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

244
00:22:02,241 --> 00:22:07,440
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

245
00:22:07,513 --> 00:22:11,916
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

246
00:22:11,984 --> 00:22:15,750
<i>Just sing.</i>

247
00:22:15,988 --> 00:22:21,153
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

248
00:22:21,226 --> 00:22:23,421
<i>The two are one</i>

249
00:22:23,529 --> 00:22:29,798
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

250
00:22:30,302 --> 00:22:35,399
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

251
00:22:39,632 --> 00:22:40,894
Sakura!

252
00:22:41,267 --> 00:22:42,757
Do you know where
Kakashi Sensei is?

253
00:22:42,836 --> 00:22:43,427
Naruto...

254
00:22:43,503 --> 00:22:46,836
I'm gonna have him watch
my training until the main tournament.

255
00:22:47,073 --> 00:22:50,133
Kakashi Sensei is probably with Sasuke.

256
00:22:50,243 --> 00:22:53,235
What's up with you, Sakura?
You seem a little down.

257
00:22:53,346 --> 00:22:54,677
No, nothing...

258
00:22:54,781 --> 00:22:57,477
It's just that I get this bad feeling...

259
00:22:57,917 --> 00:23:01,751
Next episode: "A Shadow in Darkness:
Danger Approaches Sasuke

260
00:23:01,821 --> 00:23:04,119
I feel uneasy for some reason...
